posting_body: ['YES, WE ARE OPEN!', 'CALL NOW TO SCHEDULE AN IN-PERSON TOUR!', 'OR LET US SHOW YOU THROUGH FACETIME!', "Conveniently located in Westminster, Colorado, halfway between Denver's central business district and Boulder County and ensconced against breathtaking and idyllic mountain scenery, Westcliff Apartments will not disappoint!", "Featuring one, two and three bedroom apartment homes with stainless steel appliances, upgraded kitchens and the largest square footage in the area, Westcliff is Westminster's premiere apartment community.", 'Call or visit us today!', 'Amenities Include:', 'Game Room', 'Strength and Cardio Center', 'Library & Reading Lounge', 'Built-in Bookcases', '5-hole miniature golf course', 'Fireplaces in 2nd and 3rd story homes', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Gazebo with a Fire Pit & Gas Grill', 'Ceiling Fans in Bedrooms and Living Rooms', 'Short-Term Lease Available', 'Wine Room', 'Large Walk-in Closets', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
